title: [Blighted Forest, Cliff]
description: The path dead-ends, blocked by the sheer drop-off of a cliff.  Hundreds of spans below, the forest continues, stretching to the horizon in a seemingly endless expanse of black-leafed trees.  Bats wheel overhead in the moonlight, using their high-pitched squeaks to navigate.

The path dead-ends, blocked by the sheer drop-off of a cliff.  Hundreds of spans below, the forest continues, stretching to the horizon in a seemingly endless expanse of black-leafed trees.  Eagles wheel overhead, sending their mournful echoes into the heavens.
